# ⚙️ Workflow Layer (Optional)

Use workflows only for complex AI orchestration.

Examples

* Recursive Document Processing
* Batch Embeddings
* Hybrid Retrieval Pipelines
* Agent Loops
* Evaluations

Simple CRUD should never require workflow files.

Recommended:

* LangGraph
* State Machines

